mistral.reason: Quicksand (2003 film) was not produced by Artisan Entertainment. It was produced before Lions Gate Entertainment Corporation acquired Artisan in December 2003.

qwen2.5.reason: The context information indicates that Artisan Entertainment was acquired by Lions Gate Entertainment Corporation in 2003. Therefore, Quicksand (2003 film) would have been distributed under the Lions Gate banner after the acquisition date of December 15, 2003.
